{"tid":1862840,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"poly hall友認真勸你地quit hall","createTime":"2020-02-04T23:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T08:46:07.000Z","uid":137078,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fea6105b8e8e78c5bed749c46e1c166ed5beb0b","tid":1862840,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:49:17.000Z","msg":"睇返新增嘅確診個案 <br />\n黃埔花園死咗個個傳染埋佢屋企人<br />\n特別紅土出現咗本土傳染個案<br />\n好大機會呢區有隱形肺炎患者不斷播毒<br />\n<br />\n加埋hall 又多支那人<br />\n份申報表廢到嘔，唔好信啲乜鬼野隔離措施<br />\n真係中招成座都會奶嘢<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家都冇學返住黎做咩，分分鐘停到四五月都返唔到，個段時間更加係高峰期<br />\n<br />\n有啲人可能交哂錢唔想蝕錢比佢，其實有得退<br />\n我1月尾已quit，問staff佢話剩低個啲日子可以退<br />\n最update SU好似同人血高層傾過話sem2全退<br />\n<br />\n唯一麻煩係搬行李返屋企個程，盡量唔好搭黨返到屋企一定即刻消毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">含撚光死全家 <br />\n人血紅磚收皮啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3c9c7ee2488978b2912ab9bb0465b8f5dabbce3","tid":1862840,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:50:04.000Z","msg":"Poly堅係窄啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8641da44712fd6a17a1ccf5f9c9a05b0ef85a994","tid":1862840,"uid":40867,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔得!!<br />\n<br />\n我嘅u life...ulife!!!!<br />\n係不容侵犯!!!<br />\n<br />\n樓主妖言惑眾 收皮啦!!"},{"pid":"9d0be0589c14ccb6094dfc8e56582956c498369e","tid":1862840,"uid":137078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8641da44712fd6a17a1ccf5f9c9a05b0ef85a994","tid":1862840,"uid":40867,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔得!!<br />\n<br />\n我嘅u life...ulife!!!!<br />\n係不容侵犯!!!<br />\n<br />\n樓主妖言惑眾 收皮啦!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"我返屋企唔使係common見到你呢啲食女怪唱K煮嘢食<br />\n<br />\n話你知common 有支那人煮飯，唔知有冇加埋wuhan virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b3bf45fa24c64a5c25dc6f8f1c288b3a091ab","tid":1862840,"uid":